Description:
If you are detail oriented, efficient, have a high level of understanding when it comes to navigating medical information and are computer savvy, we want to meet you!
You will be working with medical documentation and participate in software tests to identify bugs, assist in technical review, and improve product. You will also use your skills with our team at our downtown Toronto location at University and Dundas.
This position is perfect for a recent university or college grad in health sciences (such as kinesiology) that would like to re-invent themselves in a technology environment.
Most of the things you’ll work on:
Work closely with our Clinical Operations team and our QA team;
Compile, sort and verify data;
Compare data with source documents, and detect technical and clinical errors;
Directly contribute in our software training and machine learning procedures;
Exceptional grammar, communication and writing skills across all forms of media
What You’ll Need:
Completion of a related program in Health Studies;
A driven but easy-going personality. This is a role for someone who wants to be part of a bigger team and can also be self-directed with their own processing data;
Technical skills including high proficiency in typing and use of Office 365;
Hunger to learn and drive change;
An analytical nature with strengths in collecting, organization, and disseminating significant amounts of information with a high level of detail and accuracy;
A logical approach to problem solving with the instinct to follow or develop processes;
A team player who loves to collaborate - you understand that giving/getting feedback is crucial in your development and growth;
Extreme ownership: you find a problem, you bring the solution to the finish line.
* must be flexible for shift work and available for weekend shifts
This is a contract position with potential for extension.
Contract length: 3 months
Expected Start Date: 2022-01-04
Job Types: Full-time, Contract
Salary: $16.50 per hour
Schedule:
8 hour shift
Weekend availability
